Basic Features

Alumni Registration & Login (email/phone based).

Alumni Profile Creation (Name, Batch Year, Course, Current Job/Location).

Alumni Directory – searchable and filterable by batch, course, or company.

News & Announcements – institute posts updates about events, reunions, and achievements.

Event Management – show event details and allow alumni to register.

Job/Internship Posting – alumni can share job opportunities, students can view and apply.

Feedback & Suggestions – alumni provide input to improve institute activities.

Contact/Message to Admin – simple form to reach institute admins.
